<p>Some of the videotaped lectures by fellowship recipients have been digitized and can be found in the Cornell University Lecture Series collection #8-3-3222.<extref> href=https://rmc.library.cornell.edu/EAD/htmldocs/RMA03222.html></extref></p>  </relatedmaterial>
